phrases: The S Class Wizard Advancement Exam has finally started!
Both Erza and Mira passed this exam to become S Class Wizards, did not they?
And the first test finished, but...
It was hard right off the bat.
So, what was the second test again?
It was searching for the founding Master, Mavis's grave.
But a weirdo went and barged in on us!
You are gettin' in the way of the exam, damn you!
What kind of magic does Mest-san use?
Ah yes, I suppose you are not yet aware.
You do not know either, Erza-san?
What do you mean that Mest might not be a member of the guild?
It was just a hunch at first.
the more doubts I have, the more clear my knowledge of Mest becomes.
I do not follow you in the slightest.
The knowledge I have of him, even though I just joined the guild...
He is the disciple of Mystogan, the Prince.
He was chosen to take the S Class Exam last year, but unfortunately failed.
Any other information on him is cloudy and vague...
See why I told her not to partner with that weirdo!
I have never seen this kind of flower before!
I want to know what these strange flowers taste like!
Please do not eat the flowers!
Are not we heading to the top?
But I are not going to be satisfied until I give that bastard
who did this to Igneel's scarf a taste of my fist!
You are going to search for the grave while also searching for that guy?
Just choose one or the other...
I am going to do both at once, geez!
That is Natsu for you, I guess.
It is the same magic as yours!
That magic is Eastern Solid Script!
I cannot hear his steps with all the noise!
The noise has gone back to normal!
Did your writing cancel out mine?
He is cutting my iron scales like they are nothing?!
If they are all as weak as these two,
I bet we can finish them all off before the main force arrives.
Looks like he is still alive-peron.
The main force is the full might of our Guild, Grimoire Heart!
This is not just some war.
It is going to be way bigger than that.
Go and tell everyone about this, on the double!
I can handle these chumps fine on my own!
What the hell are you doing?
Just makes the hunt more fun-peron.
An all-out war against Fairy Tail, is it?
I will show you that picking a fight with Fairy Tail was a mistake!
You are going to taste the same fear!
The full force of Grimoire Heart is coming to attack!
But I have to tell everyone!
You think my forged iron is going to lose to that rusty blade?!
Where did you get those injuries?
Making an enemy of Fairy Tail...
These guys are the same as I was back then...
Gajeel was once part of another guild.
They kidnapped Lucy, and drove Fairy Tail into a corner,
but were completely defeated and Phantom Lord was destroyed.
Their various wizards all set out and went their separate ways, but...
What the hell are you here for?
Juvia entered my guild the other day.
Yeah, and she is pretty worried about you.
What the hell is that rain woman thinking?
What are you going to do now?
Well, I will get by somehow.
Can I ask you a question?
What were you thinking when you picked a fight with us?
What did Phantom Lord mean to you?
What did the guild mean to you?
What did being a wizard mean to you?
That is more than one question.
I am asking what do you, yourself, think about who you are?
Would you have taken people's lives if Jose had ordered you to?
You see, that is no different than being a puppet.
But I do not think you are as boring a man as that.
There is no need to throw yourself into the darkness.
There are people in this world who prefer solitude.
But there is no one who can withstand it.
I am the one who destroyed your guild!
Let us put all that aside.
But if I ignored a young man trying to throw himself into the darkness,
it would be myself I could never forgive.
This is not me saving you.
I am simply showing you the path to tomorrow.
Will you go forward, or will you stop?
It is up to you to decide.
I told you I could handle'them by myself...
The main force will be here any moment!
Wizards far out of my league are coming!
It is called off for now, with this.
Is it that guy from before?
That is a signal that means an enemy is coming to attack.
I do not know who or what they are,
but they think they can pick a fight with us?
I will turn the tables on'them!
Even though I wish to drop out of the guild...
You have got to be kidding me!
Why are the two of you here?
This is no time for exams.
Let us head to the emergency gathering area.
We do not have enough information now.
Erza-san, what should we do now?
For now, let us search for Mest and Wendy.
It is possible they are lost and do not know where the camp is.
I will take Gajeel to the camp.
A shrimp like you should not push herself.
You sure talk big for a guy who cannot stand up.
Juvia wants to see Gray-sama very soon!
Now then, let us hear what you are after.
You think I would talk to the likes of you?
Zeref is here on this island!
Zeref lived hundreds of years ago...
There is no way he is alive!
He is been alive these past 400 years!
But Master Hades says that he is currently sleeping.
I cannot believe what you are saying.
this world will be bathed in pure darkness!
This is Fairy Tail holy ground!
You are telling me you plan to run rampant on this divinely protected Fairy island?!
Master Hade's personal guard will be here soon.
You would do well not to underestimate the 7 Kin of Purgatory!
And the final one is already on this island...
Mest-san, what does that signal flare mean again?
You really should not try to put everything in your mouth.
Should I make my move before the main forces come?
Get away from him right away!
Mystogan would not have taken on a disciple in this world.
You did well choosing to use a human who is no longer in this world,
but your cover story was too weak, Mest.
If that is your real name.
A bunch of guys I do not know are comin' here!
Why would a Dark Guild be here?
Maybe this is also part of the S Class exam?
Like a big festival, testing our strength?
And wait, we have gone from exams to festivals?
Oh, it is not a festival!
Then I guess they are enemies.
That means I can blast'them, right?
But try not to get blasted yourself,'kay?
